description.narrative: UNICEF continued to maintain a robust presence in public communications and used numerous opportunities and various platforms to advocate for children. UNICEF has continued to be a lead organization in C4D and will continue to provide leadership in the new Country Programm (2020-2025)e. For the new Country Programme, UNICEF has developed a multi-sectoral C4D strategy focusing on four flagship result areas and other priority areas that will benefit children of Ethiopia. UNICEF will continue to focus on building the C4D capacity at all levels to achieve more results for children in the next five years. | Status:Met | As-of Date:30/06/2020
